    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Definimos en Sage la relaci√≥n de recurrencia:</p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">
a_{n}=2(a_{n-1}-a_{n-2}), n\geq2.
</script>

<p>con condiciones iniciales</p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">
a_{0}=1,\qquad a_{1}=2.
</script>

<div class="sage"><script type="text/x-sage">
def a(n):
    if n==0:
	return 1
    elif n==1:
	return 2
    else:
	return 2*(a(n-1)-a(n-2))
</script></div>

<p>Calculemos:</p>

<div class="sage"><script type="text/x-sage">
a(4)
</script></div>

<div class="sage"><script type="text/x-sage">
for i in range(30): print a(i)
</script></div>
